{
  "texts": [
    "Sixty-six questions remained at this stage.",
    "Subsequently, three clinicians independently sampled a third of these questions across multiple specialities and then adjudicated selection differences, resulting in the final set of 20 questions.",
    "Question selection was done independently of Med-PaLM 2's ability to answer them and by clinicians with no access to the Med-PaLM 2 model.",
    "Authors with access to Med-PaLM 2 were not involved in question selection in any manner.",
    "For Med-PaLM, the base LLM was PaLM 19."
  ]
}